{"tid":533854,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"係咪每個人都會認到 ...","createTime":"2018-01-19T08:34:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-20T06:43:42.000Z","uid":50321,"like":97,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"2c893fefaa15930f315bdb624bcb9f7ff66e62da","tid":533854,"uid":50321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T08:34:44.000Z","msg":"自己屋企人啲聲音 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔剩係講嘢嗰種，仲有平時啲腳步聲 飲水聲 拖鞋聲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n細個嗰陣成日趁啊爸啊媽出街就開電腦玩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一聽到鎖匙開門聲就心諗仆街啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後就認到：<br />\n開得快同順就係老母 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要即刻關機做功課<br />\n開得慢但順就係老豆 通常唔理我做緊咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n開得慢又卡卡地就係啊哥家姐 雖然會屌你幾句 但扮下死狗咁又可以繼續玩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n近排成日都聽到老母好夜起身去廚房廁所，可能身體差咗咁 ... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有一輪唔係屋企訓 一返去聽到啲聲就覺得好懷念 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5bf740fba47fd9666ca215346af978e9e874a58","tid":533854,"uid":80719,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T09:09:27.000Z","msg":"fam...family comes first..."},{"pid":"551c8323a45a5c9eace1d3911c00eca2e3ba1cd5","tid":533854,"uid":149179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T09:11:14.000Z","msg":"唔會"},{"pid":"29aec8cb28c40a27257924590c1ddcb332c1359e","tid":533854,"uid":66943,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T09:24:08.000Z","msg":"個人毒到某個lv嗰陣真係得"},{"pid":"431105cd4785da62b9d997f0e3d70ee1c5ab6284","tid":533854,"uid":165024,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T09:26:09.000Z","msg":"我連隔離屋啲聲都認到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\